The paper discusses the implementation of a secure Cloud Data Server for e-business, which involves topics related to cryptography, network security, distributed systems, and database management. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture).
